      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、ライブの翌日なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ even though it's the day after the live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、相変わらずタフやねえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ you're always so tough‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（凄い、瑠依さん昨日ライブだったのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Wow‚ Rui-san had a live yesterday…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "（少しも疲れてない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She doesn't seem tired at all…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "（……違う、疲れを見せない、んだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…No‚ she doesn't show her tiredness…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱりあの人は別格……。トップを獲れる人……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She's truly exceptional… a person who can reach the top…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お疲れ様。雫ちゃんも今からレッスン？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Shizuku-chan‚ are you going to have a lesson now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 300.00000000000426
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "…………雫ちゃん、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Shizuku-chan‚ what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ご、ごめん。気付かなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ s-sorry. I didn't notice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トリエルの練習を見てたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were watching TRINITYAiLE's practice‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "……圧倒されちゃうよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's overwhelming‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ん。凄いのは分かっていたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I knew they were amazing‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "同じ場所に立つと、もっと実感する……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we stand in the same place‚ I feel it even more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "特に瑠依さん。才能だけじゃない。凄い努力……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially Rui-san. It's not just talent. It's incredible effort…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "怖いくらい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost scary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かるよ。瑠依ちゃん、普段はあんなに優しいのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. Rui-chan is usually so kind‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
