      "text": "レッスンになると、先生より厳しいもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to lessons‚ she's stricter than the teacher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリで勝てたのは奇跡……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Winning the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix was a miracle…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "……今、勝てる気がしない。だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Right now‚ I don't feel like I can win. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1666666667,
